item.title: Need help with compiler error
item.dc:creator: @zerohero490 zerohero490
item.description:
@zerohero490 wrote:

heres a good TUT for the whole thing that will fix it for ya. been working on it forever finally finished.

welcome to my guide of how to edit and make a server
this guide is to help people start a server with a source and working compiler and everyhting they need.

                                            i would like to thank other guides before me that wrote this and creator of testscaoe and no-ip and hamachi and mopar!! give them rep too

to start off: you’ll need
a source i found that testscape is the easiest source to edit so here it is http://www.megaupload.com/?d=VC3TV8XY if you want other sources i don’t got them i’m only giving the easiest sources for beginners only. after u download this source and extract it you’ll need a working compiler luckly i have one that works for testscape and other sources. the compiler is in a zip at at the bottom of this post!!. replace the compiler with your old one and right click and edit.
Code:
@echo off
COLOR 09
title zammyscape Server
“C:Program FilesJavajdk1.5.0_06injavac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:Program FilesJavajdk1.5.0_06in/java.exe” server
JAVA -Xmx1024m server
pauseyou should replace the red text part with the version of java you have “C:Program FilesJavajdk1.5.0_06injavac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:Program FilesJavajdk1.5.0_06in/java.exe” server
congrats your compiler should work

next step: you’ll need either hamachi or no-ip
this 1st step is for hamachi users only
go to http://www.hamachi.cc/download/
download it and install after you install you can choose ur nickname.
open hamachi at teh bottom it should have a triangluar shape with teh options of create and existing netowrk or join an existing network. create your own netowrk with a name and a password.
minimize your hamachi and your set to go.

2nd step: no-ip
this part is for all those who want to set up a no-ip. you’ll need to go to http://www.no-ip.com/ and register an account their. after you activate your account sign in. you’ll be brought to a screen with a menu bar on the side giving you the options of

Your No-IP
Hosts / Redirects
Add
Manage
Manage Groups
Upgrade to Enhanced
Plus Managed DNS
Domain Registration
SSL Certificates
Mail
Monitoring
Squared Backup DNS
Your Account
Renew / Activate
choose to add under the host/redirects
make a hostname and choose a type of .org or info or whatever. i chose no-ip.org but you can choose whatever.
after you do that go all the way down forgetting all the other fields and click create host
after you created a host it is now time to downlaod the no-ipduc
go to the download tab on the top of the site clikc on the type of computer your using
windows
mac
linux/bsd/unix
downlaod and install it open up your no-ip and you should see your no-ip that u created earlier on the site
if you don’t then wait about 5 minutes before the no-ip will appear.

next step: open ur no-ipducv2.2.1
clikc on the check box to start your no-ip if i doesn’t work and you have hamachi you can reroute ur no-ip to work over that too.
what i did was go to options, connections, standard and i checked marked the top 2 boxes with override to hamachi if not working normal.
if yours did work without changing connection then your no-ip is set

next step: now you got a testscape source and a hamachi or no-ip. now you have all the stuff required to beable to edit and add tuts to your server and start a server.

now for editing. for those who ahve no clue where client.java is it is a text document named client when u open testscape real easy to see can’t miss it if you can’t find it well u got problems.
if you haven’t already open all .cfg’s with a textdocument
their now u have everyhting ready for u to go edit ur source.
now all you got to do is go on tutorial part of forum and do exactly what they say.

listen to this before you post i know people made guides before me but i spent awhile on this one and i give credit to the others before me.!

if this guide doesn’t help you please im me or messange me i’ll help u out further. have fun

congrats you are now prepared to edit and run your own server!!!
